<li id="cite_note-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMonet2021" class="citation thesis cs1">Monet, Morgan (July 29, 2021). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://scholarsarchive.byu.edu/etd/9148"><i><span></span>'It's Like Being Pulled in Two Directions': Experiences of Transgender Latter-day Saints</i></a> (Master of Science thesis). <a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young_University" title="Brigham Young University">Brigham Young University</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Adissertation&amp;rft.title=%27It%27s+Like+Being+Pulled+in+Two+Directions%27%3A+Experiences+of+Transgender+Latter-day+Saints&amp;rft.degree=Master+of+Science&amp;rft.inst=Brigham+Young+University&amp;rft.date=2021-07-29&amp;rft.aulast=Monet&amp;rft.aufirst=Morgan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fscholarsarchive.byu.edu%2Fetd%2F9148&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGender+minorities+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
