<li id="cite_note-41"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-41">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFChristensen2023" class="citation news cs1">Christensen, Jen (June 28, 2023). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/06/28/health/transgender-suicide-risk/index.html">"Transgender people face significantly higher suicide risk, Danish study finds"</a>. <a href="/wiki/CNN" title="CNN">CNN</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 10,</span> 2024</span>. <q>The study of more than 6.6 million people found that those who identified as trans had 7.7 times the rate of suicide attempts and 3.5 times the rate of suicide deaths than the broader Danish population.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Transgender+people+face+significantly+higher+suicide+risk%2C+Danish+study+finds&amp;rft.date=2023-06-28&amp;rft.aulast=Christensen&amp;rft.aufirst=Jen&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F06%2F28%2Fhealth%2Ftransgender-suicide-risk%2Findex.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGender+minorities+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
