<li id="cite_note-Preference-67"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Preference_67-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Preference_67-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFPhillips1993" class="citation thesis cs1">Phillips, Richard D. (1993). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://digitalcommons.usu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=3518&amp;context=etd"><i>Prophets and Preference: Constructing and Maintaining a Homosexual Identity in the Mormon Church</i></a> (Master of Sociology thesis). <a href="/wiki/Utah_State_University" title="Utah State University">Utah State University</a>. pp.&#160;69, 76.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Adissertation&amp;rft.title=Prophets+and+Preference%3A+Constructing+and+Maintaining+a+Homosexual+Identity+in+the+Mormon+Church&amp;rft.degree=Master+of+Sociology&amp;rft.inst=Utah+State+University&amp;rft.date=1993&amp;rft.aulast=Phillips&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+D.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fdigitalcommons.usu.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D3518%26context%3Detd&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGender+minorities+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
