<li id="cite_note-68"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-68">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWatermanKagel1998" class="citation book cs1">Waterman, Bryan; Kagel, Brian (1998). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://signaturebookslibrary.org/the-lords-university-08/"><i>The Lord's University: Freedom and Authority at BYU</i></a>. <a href="/wiki/Signature_Books" title="Signature Books">Signature Books</a>. p.&#160;341. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-56085-117-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-56085-117-2"><bdi>978-1-56085-117-2</bdi></a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">November 21,</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Lord%27s+University%3A+Freedom+and+Authority+at+BYU&amp;rft.pages=341&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-56085-117-2&amp;rft.aulast=Waterman&amp;rft.aufirst=Bryan&amp;rft.au=Kagel%2C+Brian&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fsignaturebookslibrary.org%2Fthe-lords-university-08%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGender+minorities+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
