<li id="cite_note-69"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-69">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBrown" class="citation web cs1"><a href="/wiki/Victor_L._Brown" title="Victor L. Brown">Brown, Victor</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/general-conference/1971/04/the-meaning-of-morality?lang=eng">"The Meaning of Morality"</a>. <a href="/wiki/LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="LDS Church">LDS Church</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Meaning+of+Morality&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.aulast=Brown&amp;rft.aufirst=Victor&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchofjesuschrist.org%2Fstudy%2Fgeneral-conference%2F1971%2F04%2Fthe-meaning-of-morality%3Flang%3Deng&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGender+minorities+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-LDS_Church-70"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-LDS_Church_70-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBrown_Jr.Bergin1973" class="citation book cs1">Brown Jr., Victor L.; <a href="/wiki/Allen_Bergin" title="Allen Bergin">Bergin, Allen E.</a> (1973). <i>Homosexuality: Welfare Services Packet 1</i>. <a href="/wiki/LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="LDS Church">LDS Church</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Homosexuality%3A+Welfare+Services+Packet+1&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft.aulast=Brown+Jr.&amp;rft.aufirst=Victor+L.&amp;rft.au=Bergin%2C+Allen+E.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGender+minorities+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span> The guide stated that lesbians "needs to learn feminine behavior", and the gay men "must be introduced to and learn the heterosexual or 'straight' way of life ... and what a manly priesthood leader and father does".</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-TYMO-71"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-TYMO_71-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFPacker1976" class="citation cs2"><a href="/wiki/Boyd_K._Packer" title="Boyd K. Packer">Packer, Boyd K.</a> (1976), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20160311171249/https://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/english/pdf/language-materials/33382_eng.pdf"><i>To Young Men Only</i></a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>, <a href="/wiki/LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="LDS Church">LDS Church</a>, archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/english/pdf/language-materials/33382_eng.pdf">the original</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> on March 11, 2016 &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=To+Young+Men+Only&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1976&amp;rft.aulast=Packer&amp;rft.aufirst=Boyd+K.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lds.org%2Fbc%2Fcontent%2Fshared%2Fcontent%2Fenglish%2Fpdf%2Flanguage-materials%2F33382_eng.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGender+minorities+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
